ActCanada Pension Plan Investment Board Act
PrecisReappointment of HEATHER MUNROE-BLUM, O.C., O.Q., of Montréal, Quebec, as a director of the board of directors of the Canada Pension Plan Investment Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years; and designation of HEATHER MUNROE-BLUM, O.C., O.Q., as Chairperson of the board of directors of the Canada Pension Plan Investment Board to hold office during good behaviour; effective October 27, 2014.
